<div class="language-HTML line-numbers-mode" data-ext="HTML"><pre v-pre class="language-HTML"><code>&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;path-to-javascript-file.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="variables" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#variables" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Variables</h2>
<p>As variables son o primeiro que necesitamos entender, as variables ax√∫dan a declarar o tipo de informaci√≥n que vas almacenar, podes almacenar: <strong>N√∫meros, Texto, Obxectos</strong>,... As variables se declaran usando as palabras clave <strong>var</strong> ou <strong>let</strong>.</p>
