<h2 id="loops" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#loops" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Loops</h2>
<p>Os bucles √∫sanse para recuperar unha lista de elementos e sa√≠r cando se atopa un condicional</p>
<h2 id="a-declaracion-while-mentres" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#a-declaracion-while-mentres" aria-hidden="true">#</a> A declaraci√≥n <em>while</em> - mentres</h2>
<p>Se a avaliaci√≥n cumpre a condici√≥n de expresi√≥n detense e sae do bucle. a sintaxe <strong>while</strong> √© a seguinte</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">while</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>expression<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
