</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="a-declaracion-for-in" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#a-declaracion-for-in" aria-hidden="true">#</a> A declaraci√≥n <code v-pre>for/in</code></h2>
<p>A instruci√≥n <strong><code v-pre>for/in</code></strong> √© case a mesma que a instruci√≥n <strong>for</strong> , pero <strong>for/in</strong> non require un n√∫mero de inicio, un n√∫mero final, un incremento, sen√≥n que usa o <strong>in</strong> onde vai para contar o n√∫mero de elementos que est√°n na <strong>matriz,</strong> a sintaxe √© como acompa√±amento.</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">for</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>variable <span class="token keyword">in</span> elements_array<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
<span class="token comment">//code to execute</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> 
