<h2 id="metodos-funcions" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#metodos-funcions" aria-hidden="true">#</a> M√©todos/funci√≥ns</h2>
<p>As funci√≥ns √°s veces ch√°manse m√©todos, as funci√≥ns son √∫tiles e calquera linguaxe de programaci√≥n a incl√∫e. As funci√≥ns son bloques de c√≥digo que se executan cando se chama. podes chamar √° funci√≥n que crees desde calquera parte do teu c√≥digo. A sintaxe √© a seguinte.</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code>funci√≥n <span class="token function">functionName</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>  
<span class="token comment">//Bloque de c√≥digo  </span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code>funci√≥n <span class="token function">functionName</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">parametro1<span class="token punctuation">,</span> parametro2<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>  
